<text><body>
<lb ed="T" n="0450c07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0450c08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0450c09" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 724</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0450c10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說罪業<note place="foot text" n="0450007" type="orig" resp="Taisho">應報＝報應【明】＊</note><note n="0450007" type="mod" resp="CBETA">應報【大】＊，報應【明】＊</note><app n="0450007"><lem wit="【大】">應報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">報應</rdg></app>教化地獄經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0450c11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0450c12" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0450008" place="foot text">〔後漢…譯〕十字－【元】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0450008">（後漢…譯）十字【大】，〔－〕【元】</note><app cb:word-count="10" n="0450008"><lem wit="【大】">後漢<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0450009" place="foot text">〔安息三藏〕－【宋】【宮】，安息＋（國）【明】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0450009">安息三藏【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->安息＋（國）【明】</note><app n="0450009"><lem wit="【大】">安息三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">安息國三藏</rdg></app>安世高譯</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></byline>
<lb ed="T" n="0450c13"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0450c1301">如是我聞：</p><p xml:id="pT17p0450c1305" rend="inline">一時佛住王舍城耆闍崛山中，與
<lb n="0450c14" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" n="0450010" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔大〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0450010">大【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450010"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩摩訶薩及聲聞眷屬俱，亦與比丘、比
<lb ed="T" n="0450c15"/>丘尼、優婆塞、優婆夷及諸天、龍、鬼神等皆悉
<lb ed="T" n="0450c16"/>集會。爾時信相菩薩白佛言：「<note n="0450011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0450011">世尊【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450011"><lem wit="【大】">世尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>！今有地
<lb ed="T" n="0450c17"/>獄、餓鬼、畜生、奴婢、貧富、貴賤種類若干，唯願
<lb n="0450c18" ed="T"/>世尊具演說法！若有眾生聞佛說法，如孩子
<lb ed="T" n="0450c19"/>得母、如病得醫、如<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0450012" place="foot text">羸得食＝裸得衣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">羸得食【大】，裸得衣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450012"><lem wit="【大】">羸得食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">裸得衣</rdg></app>、如暗得燈，世尊
<lb ed="T" n="0450c20"/>說法利益眾生亦復如是。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0450c21"/><p xml:id="pT17p0450c2101">爾時世尊觀時已至，見斯菩薩勸請慇懃，即
<lb ed="T" n="0450c22"/>放眉間白毫相光照于世界——地獄休息，苦痛
<lb ed="T" n="0450c23"/>安寧。爾時一切受罪眾生尋佛光明，來詣佛
<lb n="0450c24" ed="T"/>所；遶佛七匝，為佛作禮；勸請世尊，敷演道化，
<lb n="0450c25" ed="T"/>令此眾生得蒙解脫。</p>
<lb n="0450c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0450c2601">爾時信相菩薩為諸眾生而作發起，前白佛
<lb n="0450c27" ed="T"/>言：「世尊！今有受罪眾生，為諸獄卒剉碓斬身，
<lb n="0450c28" ed="T"/>從<note place="foot text" n="0450013" resp="Taisho" type="orig">頭至足＝足斬之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">頭至足【大】，足斬之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450013"><lem wit="【大】">頭至足</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">足斬之</rdg></app>乃至其頂；斬之已訖，<note n="0450014" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">巧＝旋【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0450014">巧【大】，旋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450014"><lem wit="【大】">巧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">旋</rdg></app>風吹活，
<lb ed="T" n="0450c29"/>而復斬之。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0450c2909" rend="inline">佛言：「以前<note place="foot text" n="0450015" type="orig" resp="Taisho">世＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0450015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">世【大】，身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450015"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>時<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0450016" place="foot text">坐＋（齋日殺生）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0450016">坐【大】，坐齋日殺生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0450016"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">坐齋日殺生</rdg></app>不
<pb ed="T" n="0451a" xml:id="T17.0724.0451a"/>
<lb n="0451a01" ed="T"/>信三尊、不孝父母、屠兒魁膾斬截眾生，故獲
<lb ed="T" n="0451a02"/>斯罪。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451a0203">「第二，復有眾生身體頑痺，眉鬚墮落舉
<lb n="0451a03" ed="T"/>身洪爛，鳥栖鹿宿人跡永絕，<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451001" place="foot text">沾＝砧【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451001" type="mod" resp="CBETA">沾【大】，砧【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451001"><lem wit="【大】">沾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">砧</rdg></app>污親族人不
<lb ed="T" n="0451a04"/>喜見，名<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451002" place="foot text">之＝為【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451002">之【大】，為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451002"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>癩病。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451a0411">佛言：「以前世時
<lb n="0451a05" ed="T"/>坐不信三尊、不孝父母，破壞塔寺、剝脫道
<lb n="0451a06" ed="T"/>人，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451003">斬＝斫【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451003">斬【大】，斫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451003"><lem wit="【大】">斬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斫</rdg></app>射賢聖、傷害師長，常無返復、背恩忘
<lb ed="T" n="0451a07"/>義，常行苟且、婬匿<note n="0451004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尊卑無所忌諱＝所尊不避親踈無有羞恥【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451004">尊卑無所忌諱【大】，所尊不避親踈無有羞恥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451004"><lem wit="【大】">尊卑無所忌諱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">所尊不避親踈無有羞恥</rdg></app>，故獲斯
<lb n="0451a08" ed="T"/>罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451a09"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451a0901">「第三，復有眾生身體長大，聾騃無足宛轉腹
<lb n="0451a10" ed="T"/>行，唯食泥土以自活命，為諸小蟲之所唼食，
<lb n="0451a11" ed="T"/>常受此苦不可堪處。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451a1113">佛言：「以前世
<lb ed="T" n="0451a12"/>時坐為人自用、不信好言善語，不孝父母、反戾
<lb n="0451a13" ed="T"/>時君；<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451005">或＝若【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451005">或【大】，若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451005"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">若</rdg></app>為帝<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451006">主＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">主【大】，王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451006"><lem wit="【大】">主</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>大臣、四鎮方伯、州郡令長、
<lb ed="T" n="0451a14"/><note place="foot text" n="0451007" resp="Taisho" type="orig">吏＝里【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451007">吏【大】，里【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451007"><lem wit="【大】">吏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">里</rdg></app>禁督護，恃其威勢侵奪民物，無有道理，使
<lb ed="T" n="0451a15"/>民苦悴<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451008" place="foot text">吁＝呼【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451008">吁【大】，呼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451008"><lem wit="【大】">吁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">呼</rdg></app>嗟而行。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451a16"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451a1601">「第四，復有眾生兩目盲瞎，都無所見，或<note n="0451a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">觝【CB】【麗-CB】，抵【大】</note><app n="0451a1601"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say">觝<note type="cf1">K19n0781_p0870c19</note><note type="cf2">T53n2122_p0796b12</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">抵</rdg></app>樹
<lb ed="T" n="0451a17"/>木或<note place="foot text" n="0451009" type="orig" resp="Taisho">墮＝陷【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451009">墮【大】，陷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451009"><lem wit="【大】">墮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">陷</rdg></app>溝坑，於時死已，更復受身亦復如
<lb ed="T" n="0451a18"/>是。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0451a1806" rend="inline">佛言：「以前世時坐不信罪福障
<lb n="0451a19" ed="T"/>佛光明，縫鷹眼合、籠繫眾生，皮囊盛頭不得
<lb ed="T" n="0451a20"/>所見。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451a2101">「第五，復有眾生<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451010" place="foot text">謇＝蹇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">謇【大】，蹇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451010"><lem wit="【大】">謇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蹇</rdg></app>吃瘖瘂，口不能言；若有所
<lb ed="T" n="0451a22"/>說，閉目舉手乃不言了。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451a2214">佛言：「以前
<lb n="0451a23" ed="T"/>世時坐誹謗三尊、輕毀聖道，論他好醜、求人
<lb ed="T" n="0451a24"/>長短，強誣良善、憎嫉賢人。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451a2501">「第六，復有眾生腹大<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451011">頸＝項【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">頸【大】，項【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451011"><lem wit="【大】">頸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">項</rdg></app>細，不能下食；若有所
<lb ed="T" n="0451a26"/>食，變<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451012">為＝成【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451012">為【大】，成【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451012"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>膿血。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0451a2610" rend="inline">佛言：「以前世時偷
<lb n="0451a27" ed="T"/>盜僧食，或為大會福食屏處偷噉；悋惜己物，
<lb ed="T" n="0451a28"/>但貪他財；<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451013">（心）＋常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451013" type="mod" resp="CBETA">常【大】，心常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451013"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心常</rdg></app>行惡<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451014">〔心〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">心【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451014"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，與人毒藥，氣息不通。
<lb n="0451a29" ed="T"/>故獲斯罪。」</p>
<pb n="0451b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0724.0451b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0451b01"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b0101">「第七，復有眾生，常為獄卒<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451015" place="foot text">熱燒＝燒熱【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451015">熱燒【大】，燒熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451015"><lem wit="【大】">熱燒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">燒熱</rdg></app>鐵釘釘<note n="0451016" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">人＝入【明】</note><note n="0451016" type="mod" resp="CBETA">人【大】，入【明】</note><app n="0451016"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0451b02"/>百節骨頭，釘之已訖自然火生，焚燒<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451017" place="foot text">身體＝其身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">身體【大】，其身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451017"><lem wit="【大】">身體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其身</rdg></app>悉
<lb ed="T" n="0451b03"/>皆焦爛。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451b0308">佛言：「以前世時坐為針灸
<lb ed="T" n="0451b04"/>醫師，針人身體不能差病；<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451018" place="foot text">誑他取財徒＝枉取他物使【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">誑他取財徒【大】，枉取他物使【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451018"><lem wit="【大】">誑他取財，徒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">枉取他物使</rdg></app>受苦
<lb ed="T" n="0451b05"/>痛，令他苦惱。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451b06"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b0601">「第八，復有眾生常在鑊湯中，為牛頭阿傍以
<lb n="0451b07" ed="T"/>三股鐵叉，<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451019" place="foot text">〔叉人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451019" type="mod" resp="CBETA">叉人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451019"><lem wit="【大】">叉人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>內著鑊<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451020" place="foot text">〔湯〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451020">湯【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451020"><lem wit="【大】">湯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>中，煮之令爛，還
<lb n="0451b08" ed="T"/>復吹活而復煮之。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451b0812">佛言：「以前世時
<lb ed="T" n="0451b09"/>信邪倒見，祠祀鬼神屠殺眾生，湯灌<note n="0451021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搣＝滅【宮】＊</note><note n="0451021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搣【大】＊，滅【宮】＊</note><app n="0451021"><lem wit="【大】">搣</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>毛、鑊
<lb n="0451b10" ed="T"/>湯<note n="0451022" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">煎煮＝煮之【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451022">煎煮【大】，煮之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451022"><lem wit="【大】">煎煮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">煮之</rdg></app>，不可限量。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451b11"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b1101">「第九，復有眾生常在火城中，煻煨齊心，四門
<lb ed="T" n="0451b12"/>俱開，若欲趣向，門即<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451023">閉之＝自閉【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451023">閉之【大】，自閉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451023"><lem wit="【大】">閉之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">自閉</rdg></app>，東西馳走，不能自
<lb ed="T" n="0451b13"/>免，為火燒盡。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451b1310">佛言：「以前世時坐焚
<lb n="0451b14" ed="T"/>燒山澤、火<note n="0451024" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">煨＝燒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煨【大】，燒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451024"><lem wit="【大】">煨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">燒</rdg></app>雞子、燒他村陌，燒<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451025" place="foot text">煮＝諸【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451025">煮【大】，諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451025"><lem wit="【大】">煮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諸</rdg></app>眾生身
<lb n="0451b15" ed="T"/>爛皮剝。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451b16"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b1601">「第十，復有眾生常在雪山中，<note place="foot text" n="0451026" type="orig" resp="Taisho">（為）＋寒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">寒【大】，為寒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451026"><lem wit="【大】">寒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為寒</rdg></app>風所吹，皮肉
<lb ed="T" n="0451b17"/>剝裂，求死不得。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0451b1711" rend="inline">佛言：「以前世時
<lb ed="T" n="0451b18"/>坐橫道作賊，剝脫人衣，使冬月之日令他凍
<lb n="0451b19" ed="T"/>死；<note place="foot text" n="0451027" type="orig" resp="Taisho">生㓟牛羊＝或復生剝牛羊皮【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451027">生㓟牛羊【大】，或復生剝牛羊皮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451027"><lem wit="【大】">生㓟牛羊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">或復生剝牛羊皮</rdg></app>痛不可堪。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b2001">「第十一，復有眾生常在刀山、劍樹上，若有所
<lb ed="T" n="0451b21"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451028">投＝捉【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451028">投【大】，捉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451028"><lem wit="【大】">投</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">捉</rdg></app>，即便割傷，<note place="foot text" n="0451029" type="orig" resp="Taisho">支＝枝【宋】【宮】，肢【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451029">支【大】，枝【宋】【宮】，肢【元】【明】</note><app n="0451029"><lem wit="【大】">支</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">枝</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">肢</rdg></app>節斷壞。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451b2114">佛言：「以
<lb n="0451b22" ed="T"/>前世時<note n="0451030" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔坐〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451030">坐【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451030"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>屠殺為業，烹害眾生，屠割剝<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451031">裂＝切【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">裂【大】，切【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451031"><lem wit="【大】">裂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0451b23" ed="T"/>骨肉分離，頭脚星散，懸於高格，稱量而賣；或
<lb n="0451b24" ed="T"/>復生懸眾生苦痛難處。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b2501">「第十二，復有眾生五根不具。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0451b2516" rend="inline">佛言：
<lb n="0451b26" ed="T"/>「以前世時坐飛鷹走狗彈射禽獸，或斷其頭，
<lb ed="T" n="0451b27"/>或斷其足，生<app corresp="#0451021" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">搣</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>鳥翼。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451b2801">「第十三，復有眾生，攣躄背僂，腰髖不<note place="foot text" n="0451032" type="orig" resp="Taisho">遂＝隨【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遂【大】，隨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451032"><lem wit="【大】">遂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">隨</rdg></app>，脚跛
<lb n="0451b29" ed="T"/>手<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451033" place="foot text">拘＝折【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">拘【大】，折【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451033"><lem wit="【大】">拘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">折</rdg></app>，不能操涉。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451b2911">佛言：「以前世時
<pb xml:id="T17.0724.0451c" ed="T" n="0451c"/>
<lb n="0451c01" ed="T"/>坐為人憯剋，行道安槍；或安射<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451034" place="foot text">窠＝弋羅【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451034">窠【大】，弋羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451034"><lem wit="【大】">窠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">弋羅</rdg></app>，施張弶穽
<lb n="0451c02" ed="T"/>陷墜眾生，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451035">〔頭破脚折〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭破脚折【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451035"><lem wit="【大】">頭破脚折</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，傷損非一。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0451c03"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451c0301">「第十四，復有眾生，常為獄卒桎梏其身，不得
<lb n="0451c04" ed="T"/>免脫。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451c0407">佛言：「以前世時坐<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451036">網捕眾生籠＝抄劫人糧食枷【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451036">網捕眾生籠【大】，抄劫人糧食枷【宮】</note><app n="0451036"><lem wit="【大】">網捕眾
<lb ed="T" n="0451c05"/>生，<note place="foot text" n="0451037" resp="Taisho" type="orig">籠＋（枷鎖）【三】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451037">籠【大】，籠枷鎖【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0451037"><lem wit="【大】">籠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">籠枷鎖</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">抄劫人糧食枷</rdg></app>繫而畜，<note place="foot text" n="0451038" resp="Taisho" type="orig">〔飢窮困苦〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飢窮困苦【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451038"><lem wit="【大】">飢窮困苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；或為<note place="foot text" n="0451039" type="orig" resp="Taisho">宰＝帝【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451039">宰【大】，帝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451039"><lem wit="【大】">宰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">帝</rdg></app>主、令長貪
<lb n="0451c06" ed="T"/>取<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451040" place="foot text">財錢＝民錢財【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451040" type="mod" resp="CBETA">財錢【大】，民錢財【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451040"><lem wit="【大】">財錢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">民錢財</rdg></app>，枉繫良善，怨<note n="0451041" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">苦號＝酷呼【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451041">苦號【大】，酷呼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451041"><lem wit="【大】">苦號</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">酷呼</rdg></app>天，不得<note place="foot text" n="0451042" resp="Taisho" type="orig">縱＝從【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縱【大】，從【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451042"><lem wit="【大】">縱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">從</rdg></app>意。故
<lb ed="T" n="0451c07"/>獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451c0801">「第十五，復有眾生或癲、或狂、或癡、或騃，不別
<lb n="0451c09" ed="T"/>好醜。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451c0907">佛言：「以前世時<note place="foot text" n="0451043" type="orig" resp="Taisho">坐＋（耽荒嗜酒無有度量）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451043">坐【大】，坐耽荒嗜酒無有度量【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451043"><lem wit="【大】">坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">坐耽荒嗜酒無有度量</rdg></app>飲酒醉
<lb ed="T" n="0451c10"/>亂，犯三十六失，後得癡身如似醉人，不識尊
<lb ed="T" n="0451c11"/>卑<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451044" place="foot text">〔不別〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451044" type="mod" resp="CBETA">不別【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451044"><lem wit="【大】">不別</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>好醜。<note n="0451045" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔八萬…過犯〕六十四字－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451045">（八萬…過犯）六十四字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451045" cb:word-count="64"><lem wit="【大】">八萬劫墮沸屎地獄，獄卒斬
<lb n="0451c12" ed="T"/>剉，求死不得求生不得，五窮六極長夜受苦，
<lb ed="T" n="0451c13"/>以坐貪酒過。受罪已，始得為人，癃殘跛蹇，為
<lb n="0451c14" ed="T"/>人之所憎嫉；行逢接他橫事，常無樂時。以酒
<lb n="0451c15" ed="T"/>過犯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451c1601">「第十六，復有眾生其形甚小，陰藏甚大；挽之
<lb ed="T" n="0451c17"/>身<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451046">疲＝皮【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451046">疲【大】，皮【宮】</note><app n="0451046"><lem wit="【大】">疲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">皮</rdg></app>，皆復進引；行<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0451047">立＝步【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0451047">立【大】，步【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451047"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">步</rdg></app>坐臥，以之為妨。何罪
<lb ed="T" n="0451c18"/>所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0451c1803">佛言：「以前世時坐治生販賣，自譽己物，
<lb n="0451c19" ed="T"/>毀<note n="0451048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呰他財囂＝辱他物矯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451048" type="mod" resp="CBETA">呰他財囂【大】，辱他物矯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451048"><lem wit="【大】">呰他財；囂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">辱他物矯</rdg></app>升弄㪷，<note place="foot text" n="0451049" resp="Taisho" type="orig">躡＝捻【明】</note><note n="0451049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">躡【大】，捻【明】</note><app n="0451049"><lem wit="【大】">躡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">捻</rdg></app>秤前後，<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0451050">〔欺誑於人〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0451050">欺誑於人【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0451050"><lem wit="【大】">欺誑於人</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。
<lb n="0451c20" ed="T"/>故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0451c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0451c2101">「第十七，復有眾生男根不具，為黃門身，不得
<lb n="0451c22" ed="T"/><note n="0451051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妻娶＝娶妻【三】【宮】</note><note n="0451051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妻娶【大】，娶妻【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0451051"><lem wit="【大】">妻娶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">娶妻</rdg></app>。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0451c2207" rend="inline">佛言：「以前世時坐喜犍象、
<lb ed="T" n="0451c23"/>馬、牛、羊、猪、狗，不可稱數，令此眾生苦痛難忍，
<lb ed="T" n="0451c24"/>死而復穌。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<pb xml:id="T17.0724.0452a" n="0452a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0452a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0452a0101">「第十八，復有眾生從生至老，無有兒子孤立
<lb ed="T" n="0452a02"/>獨存。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0452a0207" rend="inline">佛言：「以前世時坐為人暴惡，
<lb n="0452a03" ed="T"/>不信罪福；百鳥產乳之時，齎持瓶器，<note n="0452001" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">循＝順【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452001">循【大】，順【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452001"><lem wit="【大】">循</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">順</rdg></app>大水
<lb n="0452a04" ed="T"/>渚，求拾鴻鵠、鸚鵡、鵝、<note place="foot text" n="0452002" resp="Taisho" type="orig">鴈＝鷹【宮】</note><note n="0452002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鴈【大】，鷹【宮】</note><app n="0452002"><lem wit="【大】">鴈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">鷹</rdg></app>諸鳥子卵，擔歸煮
<lb ed="T" n="0452a05"/>噉；諸鳥失子，悲鳴叫裂，眼中血出。故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0452a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0452a0601">「第十九，復有眾生少小孤寒，無有父母、兄弟，
<lb n="0452a07" ed="T"/>為他作使，辛苦活命；長大成人，橫<note n="0452003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝罹【明】＊</note><note n="0452003" type="mod" resp="CBETA"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->罹【CB】【明】＊，羅【大】＊</note><app n="0452003"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">罹</lem><rdg wit="【大】">羅</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">罹</rdg></app>殃禍，縣
<lb ed="T" n="0452a08"/>官所縛，繫閉牢獄；無人追餉，飢窮困苦，無所
<lb ed="T" n="0452a09"/>告及。何罪所致？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0452a0907">佛言：「以前世時坐喜<note n="0452004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔捕〕－【宮】</note><note n="0452004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捕【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0452004"><lem wit="【大】">捕</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0452a10" ed="T"/>拾鵰、鷲、<note place="foot text" n="0452005" type="orig" resp="Taisho">鷹＋（鶴鶁）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0452005">鷹【大】，鷹鶴鶁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452005"><lem wit="【大】">鷹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鷹鶴鶁</rdg></app>、鷂、熊、羆、虎、豹，枷鎖而畜，孤此眾生，
<lb ed="T" n="0452a11"/>父母、兄弟常恒憂念，悲鳴叫裂，哀感人心；不
<lb n="0452a12" ed="T"/>能供<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452006" place="foot text">養＝食【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452006">養【大】，食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452006"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>，常苦飢餓，骨立皮連，求死不得。故獲
<lb n="0452a13" ed="T"/>斯罪。」</p>
<lb n="0452a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0452a1401">「第二十，復有眾生其形甚醜，身體黑如漆，兩
<lb ed="T" n="0452a15"/><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452007">目＝耳【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0452007">目【大】，耳【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452007"><lem wit="【大】">目</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耳</rdg></app>復青，頭頰俱<note n="0452008" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">垖＝搥【宮】</note><note n="0452008" type="mod" resp="CBETA">垖【大】，搥【宮】</note><app n="0452008"><lem wit="【大】">垖</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">搥</rdg></app>，<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452009" place="foot text">皰＝胞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皰【大】，胞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452009"><lem wit="【大】">皰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">胞</rdg></app>面平鼻，兩<note place="foot text" n="0452010" type="orig" resp="Taisho">目＝眼【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0452010">目【大】，眼【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452010"><lem wit="【大】">目</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">眼</rdg></app>黃赤，
<lb ed="T" n="0452a16"/>牙齒踈缺，口氣腥臭，矬短<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0452011" place="foot text">癰＝擁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癰【大】，擁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452011"><lem wit="【大】">癰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">擁</rdg></app>腫，大腹<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452012">腰＝凸【三】，胅【宮】</note><note n="0452012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">腰【大】，凸【宋】【元】【明】，胅【宮】</note><app n="0452012"><lem wit="【大】">腰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">凸</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">胅</rdg></app>髖，
<lb ed="T" n="0452a17"/>脚復繚戾，僂脊<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452013">匡＝曲【三】</note><note n="0452013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">匡【大】，曲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452013"><lem wit="【大】">匡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">曲</rdg></app>肋，費衣健<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0452014">食＋（言語失則行步勤貸）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，食言語失則行步勤貸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452014"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食言語失則行步勤貸</rdg></app>，惡瘡膿血、
<lb ed="T" n="0452a18"/>水腫乾<note place="foot text" n="0452015" resp="Taisho" type="orig">痟＝消【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452015">痟【大】，消【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452015"><lem wit="【大】">痟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">消</rdg></app>、疥癩癰疽種種諸惡集在其身；
<lb ed="T" n="0452a19"/>雖親附人，人不在意；若他作罪，橫羅其殃；永
<lb n="0452a20" ed="T"/>不見佛、永不聞法、永不識僧。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0452a2016" rend="inline">佛
<lb ed="T" n="0452a21"/>言：「以前世時坐為子不孝父母，為臣不忠其
<lb n="0452a22" ed="T"/>君，為君不敬其下，朋友不以其信，鄉黨不以
<lb n="0452a23" ed="T"/>其齒，朝廷不以其爵；趣為趣作，心意顛倒，無
<lb ed="T" n="0452a24"/>有其度；不信三尊，殺君害師；伐國掠民、攻城
<lb n="0452a25" ed="T"/>破塢、偷寨過盜，惡業非一；美己惡人，侵<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0452016">陵＝凌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陵【大】，凌【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452016"><lem wit="【大】">陵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">凌</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0452a26"/>孤老，誣謗賢<note n="0452017" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">聖＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">聖【大】，善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452017"><lem wit="【大】">聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善</rdg></app>，輕慢尊長，欺誑下賤。一切罪
<lb ed="T" n="0452a27"/>業<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452018" place="foot text">悉＝皆【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452018">悉【大】，皆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452018"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">皆</rdg></app>具犯之。眾惡集報，故獲斯罪。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0452a28"/><p xml:id="pT17p0452a2801">爾時一切<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452019">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452019">諸【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452019"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>受罪眾生聞佛作如是說，<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452020">悲㘁＝號泣【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0452020">悲㘁【大】，號泣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452020"><lem wit="【大】">悲
<lb ed="T" n="0452a29"/>㘁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號泣</rdg></app>動地，淚下如雨，而白佛言：「唯願世尊久住
<pb xml:id="T17.0724.0452b" n="0452b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0452b01" ed="T"/>說法，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0452021">令＝化【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452021"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化</rdg></app>我等輩<note n="0452022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝令【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而【大】，令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452022"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>得解脫！」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0452b0111">佛言：「若我久住，
<lb ed="T" n="0452b02"/><note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452023">薄德＝德薄【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452023" type="mod" resp="CBETA">薄德【大】，德薄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452023"><lem wit="【大】">薄德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">德薄</rdg></app>之人不種善根，謂我常在，不念無常。善
<lb ed="T" n="0452b03"/>男子！譬如孩兒，母常在側，不生難遭之想；若
<lb ed="T" n="0452b04"/>母去者，便生渴仰思戀之心；母方還來，乃生
<lb n="0452b05" ed="T"/>歡喜。善男子！我今亦復如是，知諸眾生善惡
<lb n="0452b06" ed="T"/>業緣、受報好醜，故般涅槃。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0452b0611"><note n="0452024" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">爾＝于【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0452024">爾【大】，于【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452024"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg></app>時世尊即<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452025" place="foot text">為此諸受罪眾生＝於罪眾生前【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452025">為此諸受罪眾生【大】，於罪眾生前【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452025"><lem wit="【大】">為
<lb n="0452b07" ed="T"/>此諸受罪眾生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於罪眾生前</rdg></app><note n="0452026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">面＝而【宮】</note><note n="0452026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">而【CB】【麗-CB】【宮】，面【大】</note><app n="0452026"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">而<note type="cf1">K19n0781_p0872b21</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">面</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">而</rdg></app>說偈言：</p>
<lb n="0452b08" ed="T"/><lg rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em" xml:id="lgT17p0452b0801"><l>「水流不常滿，</l><l>火盛不久然，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0452b09"/><l>日出須臾沒，</l><l>月滿已復缺。</l>
<lb n="0452b10" ed="T"/><l>尊榮豪貴者，</l><l>無常復過是，</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0452b11"/><l>念當勤精進，</l><l>頂禮無上尊。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="T" n="0452b12"/><p xml:id="pT17p0452b1201">爾時世尊說斯偈已，諸受罪眾生白佛言：「世
<lb ed="T" n="0452b13"/>尊！<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452027">修＝作【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">修【大】，作【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452027"><lem wit="【大】">修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">作</rdg></app>何善行得離斯苦？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0452b1310" rend="inline">佛言：「當勤孝順父
<lb n="0452b14" ed="T"/>母，敬事師長，歸奉三尊；勤行布施、持戒、忍辱、
<lb ed="T" n="0452b15"/>精進、禪定、智慧，慈悲喜捨，怨親平等，同己無
<lb ed="T" n="0452b16"/>二；不欺孤老，不輕下賤，護彼如己。汝等若能
<lb n="0452b17" ed="T"/>如是修行，則為已得報佛之恩，永離眾苦。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0452b1717" rend="inline">說
<lb n="0452b18" ed="T"/>是經已，菩薩摩訶薩即得阿耨多羅三藐三
<lb n="0452b19" ed="T"/>菩提，聲聞、緣覺即得六通、三明、具八解脫，有
<lb n="0452b20" ed="T"/>得法眼<note place="foot text" n="0452028" type="orig" resp="Taisho">淨＋（者）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452028">淨【大】，淨者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452028"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淨者</rdg></app>。若有眾生得聞是經不墮三塗、八
<lb n="0452b21" ed="T"/>難之處，地獄休息，苦痛安寧。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0452b2112"><note place="foot text" n="0452029" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔爾時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0452029" type="mod" resp="CBETA">爾時【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0452029"><lem wit="【大】">爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>信相菩薩
<lb ed="T" n="0452b22"/>白佛言：「當何名此經？云何奉持？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT17p0452b2213">佛告信相菩
<lb ed="T" n="0452b23"/>薩善男子：「此經名為『罪業<note place="foot text" n="0452030" resp="Taisho" type="orig">報應＝應報【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0452030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">報應【大】，應報【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0452030"><lem wit="【大】">報應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">應報</rdg></app>教化地獄經』，
<lb ed="T" n="0452b24"/>當奉持之，廣令流布，功德無量！」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0452b2413" rend="inline">諸<note place="foot text" type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="0452031">〔天〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="0452031">天【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0452031"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大眾聞
<lb n="0452b25" ed="T"/>經歡喜，五體投地，作禮奉行。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="T" n="0452b26"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><title><note place="foot text" n="0452032" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0452032" type="mod" resp="CBETA">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0452032"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>罪業<app corresp="#0450007" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">應報</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">報應</rdg></app>教化地獄經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
